{{#if model}}
<div class="row row-xs-height">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        
    </div>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="row row-xs-height">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <p class="lead">
            It appears that you don't have a group yet.  
        </p>
        <p>
            Creating a group allows you to share your posts, i.e. your private events such as birthday or an outing to a local zoo, only to this group.
        </p>
        <p>
            Let's say you have two children - Aiden is 5 and Lily is 1.  You could create two groups that include Aiden's circle of friends' families into Aiden's group, and Lily's circle of friends' families into Lily's group.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row row-xs-height">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        {{#link-to 'group.new' class="btn btn-primary"}}Add New Group{{/link-to}}
    </div>
</div>
{{/if}}
